Let's make a game!
	name:Zanzarah Clicker alpha0.0.1
	by:Lymph
	desc:Небольшая игра, позволяющая снова окунуться в мир Занзары.
	created:7/5/19
	version:0.1

Settings
    number display full
    no bulk particles
	spritesheet:iconstop, 48 by 48, https://imgur.com/EOpsJVD.png
	spritesheet:icons, 48 by 48, https://imgur.com/u2CEbRk.png
	spritesheet:icons2, 60 by 60, https://imgur.com/dJdpUxD.png
	spritesheet:elements, 48 by 48, https://imgur.com/YC0KapQ.png
