*grouprock1
class:rockfon
tag:grouprock
text: Rock Fairies 
icon:elements[2,0]
no tooltip
on click:
show Grem
show Gremor
show Gremrock
show grouprock
hide this
end
hidden

		*TEMPLATE
		on earn:yield 1 fairies
		on earn:yield 1 rock
		on earn:yield 1 grouprock
		on earn:yield 1 grouprock1
		class:fairyfon
		tag:grouprock

	*Grem
		text:[?(have this)|Grem — lvl [fairy3level]|You don't have this fairy yet!][?(have this and fairy3level<60)|, mana [fairy3mana]|] 
		tag:fairy3
		tag:grouprock
desc:</>Grems are beings which can mainly be found in stone deserts, but also in big rocks in Zanzarah. These strong beings are cowardly at first, but their courage grows with their success. He evolves into Gremor at level 30. [?(have this)|</><b>Yield: [floor(fairy3yield:ps)].[(fairy3yield:ps*pow(10,2))%pow(10,2)] gold/s, total: [fairy3yield] ([fairy3yield/gold*100]% of bank)</b>|][?(have this)|<b></>Health: [fairy3health]/[fairy3level*5]</b>|][?(have this)|</><b>Level: [fairy3level]/60</b>|][?(have this)|</><b>Mana: [floor(fairy3mana)].[(fairy3mana*pow(10,2))%pow(10,2)]/[floor(fairy3level/4)+15]</b>|][?(have this)|</><b>XP: [fairy3xp] — [floor(fairy3xp:ps)].[(fairy3xp:ps*pow(10,2))%pow(10,2)] XP/s, till next level: [fairy3xpreq-fairy3xp]</b>|]
		cost:50 gold and 1 silversphere
		icon:icons[3,5]
		// обнуление феи при покупке
		on earn:
		if (chance(1%))
		lose 1 this
		lose 1 fairies
		lose 1 water
		yield 1 silversphere
		toast This fairy escaped!
		else
		fairy3level is ceil(fairy3level*0.15)
		fairy3xp is fairy3level*fairy3level*4.17
		fairy3mana is floor(fairy3level/4)*15
		yield floor(fairy3level/4+15) fairy3mana
		yield fairy3level rocklevel
		toast You catched the fairy!
		end
		end
		on tick:
		// начисление маны
		if (have this and mana>=1 and fairy3mana<=0.1)
		lose 0.01 fairy3mana
		yield floor(fairy3level/4)+15 fairy3mana
		lose 1 mana	
		toast Grem's mana refilled. This fairy continues to work.	
		end
		end
		on click:
		// начисление золотой моркови
		if (have this and no goldencarrot and fairy3level>10 and fairy3level<=59 and fairy3mana>0.01)
		toast You don't have any golden carrots to spend.
		else if (have this and goldencarrot>=1 and fairy3level<10 and fairy3mana>0.01)
		toast Once Grem reaches 10 level you'd be able to feed this fairy with golden carrots.
		else if (have this and goldencarrot>=1 and fairy3level is 60)
		toast This fairy is already at 60 level.
		else if (have this and goldencarrot>=1 and fairy3level>=10 and fairy3level<=59 and fairy3xp>0 and fairy3xpreq-fairy3xp>1 and fairy3mana>0)
		$goldcarboost=fairy3xpreq-fairy3xp-1
		yield $goldcarboost fairy3xp
		lose 1 goldencarrot
		toast Golden Carrot was successfully spent.
		end
		end
		on tick:
		if (have this and mana is 0 and fairy3mana is 0)
		yield 0.001 fairy3mana
		toast Grem's ran out of mana. Buy some mana, so this fairy could continue to work.
		end		
		end	
		on tick:
		if (fairy3level<60 and fairy3mana>0.01)
		//потеря маны в секунду
		lose (0.045*building3)/(1+0.072*fairy3level) fairy3mana
		// скорость набора опыта
		yield 0.14*building3 fairy3xp
		end
		end
		on tick:
		// заработок опыта
		fairy3xpreq=4.17*(fairy3level+1)*(fairy3level+1)
		if (fairy3xp>=fairy3xpreq)
		yield 0.5 fairy3level
		yield 0.5 rocklevel
		toast Grem achieved [fairy3level+1] level!
		end
		end
		on tick:
		if (fairy3xp>3753 and no gremorevolve)
		show Gremor
		toast Grem is ready to evolve to Gremor. Click on the Gremor to evolve (Notice, that you are going to lose your Grem!)
		yield gremorevolve
		end
		end

	*Gremor
		text: [?(have this)|Gremor — lvl [fairy4level]|Click to evolve from Grem!] [?(have this and fairy4level<60)|, mana [fairy4mana]| ]
		tag:fairy4
		tag:grouprock
		desc:</> If a Grem metamorphoses to a Gremor, his strength, maturity and valor are increased. His good-naturedness doesn't influence his fighting, but as a companion he'll soon make friends with other fairies. He evolves into Gremrock at level 50.[?(have this)|</><b>Yield: [floor(fairy4yield:ps)].[(fairy4yield:ps*pow(10,2))%pow(10,2)] gold/s, total: [fairy4yield] ([fairy4yield/gold*100]% of bank)</b>|][?(have this)|<b></>Health: [fairy4health]/[fairy4level*5]</b>|][?(have this)|</><b>Level: [fairy4level]/60</b>|][?(have this)|</><b>Mana: [floor(fairy4mana)].[(fairy4mana*pow(10,2))%pow(10,2)]/[floor(fairy4level/4)+15]</b>|][?(have this)|</><b>XP: [fairy4xp] — [floor(fairy4xp:ps)].[(fairy4xp:ps*pow(10,2))%pow(10,2)] XP/s, till next level: [fairy4xpreq-fairy4xp]</b>|]
		icon:icons[4,5]
		on earn:
		if (have Grem and fairy3xp>=3753)
		lose Grem
		lose 1 fairies
		lose 1 rock
		fairy4level is fairy3level 
		fairy4xp is (fairy3level*fairy3level*4.17) 
		fairy4xpreq is (4.17*(fairy3level+1)*(fairy3level+1)) 
		fairy4mana is fairy3mana
		toast Grem evolved into Gremor!
		else
		lose this
		lose 1 rock
		lose 1 fairies
		end
		end
		on tick:
		// начисление маны
		if (have this and mana>=1 and fairy4mana<0.5)
		lose 0.01 fairy4mana
		yield fairy4level/4+15 fairy4mana
		lose 1 mana	
		toast Gremor's mana refilled. This fairy continues to work.	
		end
		end
		on click:
		// начисление золотой моркови
		if (have this and no goldencarrot and fairy4level>10 and fairy4level<=59 and fairy4mana>0.01)
		toast You don't have any golden carrots to spend.
		else if (have this and goldencarrot>=1 and fairy4level<10 and fairy4mana>0.01)
		toast Once Tadana reaches 10 level you'd be able to feed this fairy with golden carrots.
		else if (have this and goldencarrot>=1 and fairy4level is 60)
		toast This fairy is already at 60 level.
		else if (have this and goldencarrot>=1 and fairy4level>=10 and fairy4level<=59 and fairy4xp>0 and fairy4xpreq-fairy4xp>1 and fairy4mana>0)
		$goldcarboost=fairy4xpreq-fairy4xp-1
		yield $goldcarboost fairy4xp
		lose 1 goldencarrot
		toast Golden Carrot was successfully spent.
		end
		end
		on tick:
		if (have this and mana is 0 and fairy4mana is 0)
		yield 0.001 fairy4mana
		toast Gremor's ran out of mana. Buy some mana, so this fairy could continue to work.
		end	
		end
		on tick:
		if (fairy4level<60 and fairy4mana>0.01)
		//потеря маны в секунду
		lose (0.04*(building3))/(1+0.072*fairy4level) fairy4mana
		// скорость набора опыта
		yield 0.05*(building3) fairy4xp
		end
		end
		on tick:
		// заработок опыта
		fairy4xpreq=4.17*(fairy4level+1)*(fairy4level+1)
		if (fairy4xp>=fairy4xpreq)
		yield 0.5 fairy4level
		yield 0.5 rocklevel
		toast Gremor achieved [fairy4level+1] level!
		end
		end
		on tick:
		if (fairy4xp>10245 and no gremrockevolve)
		show Gremrock
		toast Gremor is ready to evolve to Gremrock. Click on the Gremrock to evolve. Once evolved, Gremrock will gain all the XP Gremor had and you shall lose your Gremor.
		yield gremrockevolve
		end
		end
		hidden
		req:gremorevolve or Gremrock

	*Gremrock
		text:[?(have this)|Gremrock — lvl [fairy5level]|Click to evolve from Gremor!] [?(have this and fairy5level<60)|, mana [fairy5mana]| ]
		cost:Gremor
		tag:fairy5
		tag:grouprock
		desc:</> Not only is a Gremrock a creature of dangerous appearance: unlike his evolutionary ancestors, the Grem and the Gremor, it also knows how to use its strength and power efficiently in combat.[?(have this)|</><b>Yield: [floor(fairy5yield:ps)].[(fairy5yield:ps*pow(10,2))%pow(10,2)] gold/s, total: [fairy5yield] ([fairy5yield/gold*100]% of bank)</b>|][?(have this)|<b></>Health: [fairy5health]/[fairy5level*5]</b>|][?(have this)|</><b>Level: [fairy5level]/60</b>|][?(have this)|</><b>Mana: [floor(fairy5mana)].[(fairy5mana*pow(10,2))%pow(10,2)]/[floor(fairy5level/4)+15]</b>|][?(have this)|</><b>XP: [fairy5xp] — [floor(fairy5xp:ps)].[(fairy5xp:ps*pow(10,2))%pow(10,2)] XP/s, till next level: [fairy5xpreq-fairy5xp]</b>|]
		icon:icons[5,5]
		on earn:
		lose Gremor
		lose 1 fairies
		lose 1 rock
		fairy5level is fairy4level 
		fairy5xp is (fairy4level*fairy4level*4.17) 
		fairy5xpreq is (4.17*(fairy4level+1)*(fairy4level+1)) 
		fairy5mana is fairy4mana
		toast Gremor evolved into Gremrock!
		end
		on tick:
		// начисление маны
		if (have this and mana>=1 and fairy5mana<0.5)
		lose 0.01 fairy5mana
		yield fairy5level/4+15 fairy5mana
		lose 1 mana	
		toast Gremrock's mana refilled. This fairy continues to work.	
		end
		end
		on click:
		// начисление золотой моркови
		if (have this and no goldencarrot and fairy5level>10 and fairy5level<=59 and fairy5mana>0.01)
		toast You don't have any golden carrots to spend.
		else if (have this and goldencarrot>=1 and fairy5level<10 and fairy5mana>0.01)
		toast Once Tadana reaches 10 level you'd be able to feed this fairy with golden carrots.
		else if (have this and goldencarrot>=1 and fairy5level is 60)
		toast This fairy is already at 60 level.
		else if (have this and goldencarrot>=1 and fairy5level>=10 and fairy5level<=59 and fairy5xp>0 and fairy5xpreq-fairy5xp>1 and fairy5mana>0)
		$goldcarboost=fairy5xpreq-fairy5xp-1
		yield $goldcarboost fairy5xp
		lose 1 goldencarrot
		toast Golden Carrot was successfully spent.
		end
		end
		on tick:
		if (have this and mana is 0 and fairy5mana is 0)
		yield 0.001 fairy5mana
		toast Gremrock's ran out of mana. Buy some mana, so this fairy could continue to work.
		end		
		end	
		on tick:
		if (fairy5level<60 and fairy5mana>0.01)
		// скорость набора опыта
		yield 0.04*(building3) fairy5xp
		//потеря маны в секунду
		lose (0.032*(building3))/(1+0.072*fairy5level) fairy5mana
		end
		end
		on tick:
		// заработок опыта
		fairy5xpreq=4.17*(fairy5level+1)*(fairy5level+1)
		if (fairy5xp>=fairy5xpreq)
		yield 0.5 fairy5level
		yield 0.5 rocklevel
		toast Gremrock achieved [fairy5level+1] level!
		end
		end
		req:gremrockevolve


