		lose 1 fairies
		lose 1 water
		fairy7level is fairy6level 
		fairy7xp is (fairy6level*fairy6level*4.17) 
		fairy7xpreq is (4.17*(fairy6level+1)*(fairy6level+1)) 
		fairy7mana is fairy6mana
		toast Tadana evolved into Aquana!
		else
		lose this
		lose 1 water
		lose 1 fairies
		end
		end
